52
00:04:22,028 --> 00:04:25,353
Some of you know, well, in her past life, she was called Noreen.

53
00:04:25,372 --> 00:04:30,338
And she teaches occasionally, as you know, at Satipan.

54
00:04:31,853 --> 00:04:33,915
Then we have Sister Ruth.

55
00:04:34,596 --> 00:04:47,810
Sister Ruth is also, she's an Anglican nun ordained with the Archbishop of Canterbury and is the spiritual director of a particular trust under his name.

56
00:04:49,552 --> 00:05:01,286
She also holds a lineage through Gary Roshi, Roshi John Gary, and therefore carries with her these two traditions, both the Buddhist tradition

57
