of Chan, Chinese Chan, and the Christian tradition.

58
00:05:05,019 --> 00:05:08,884
So she's right at the interface where these two monoliths appear.

59
00:05:10,767 --> 00:05:23,245
And she lives as a hermit up on the Brecon Beacons, and she was stuck for two months in the last snow down here, but with a tractor to feed her.

60
00:05:23,264 --> 00:05:24,607
Wasn't it two months?

61
00:05:24,627 --> 00:05:27,089
Something like that.

62
00:05:27,331 --> 00:05:27,911
Five weeks.

63
00:05:28,091 --> 00:05:29,112
Five weeks, about two months.

64
00:05:30,427 --> 00:05:59,403
um then there's father silouan father silouan just lives across here on the sniper stones those of you who come from uh from around here will know that and he uh he's an orthodox uh monk um and he's been up there for many years and uh obviously a great companion for me uh he's up there also working and i'm trying to get escape work down here so it's an opportunity to get together

65
